    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier acquisition for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and presenting in superior mechanical order, it offers a refined performance profile and a sophisticated aesthetic. The interior cabin reflects a history of conscientious ownership, while a comprehensive multi-point inspection confirms its structural and functional reliability. This is an exceptional opportunity to secure a high-caliber vehicle that delivers both prestige and enduring value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
